   "source": [
    "<h1><center>Heart Disease Prediction</center></h1>\n",
    "<hr>"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f9c7cbd7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<h1>Objective:</h1>\n",
    "<p>Predicting whether a person has heart disease (1) or not (0) on the basis of 13 parameters as found in the dataset 'heart_disease_data.csv' and utilizing a logistic regression model (only two labeled outcomes) as in a typical supervised learning problem.</p>\n",
    "<hr>"
   ]
  },
  {
